title: longformat
---
type: filter
---
signature: value, secs=True
---
summary: Formats the longitude into a string
---
body:

This formats a longitude in float format into a human readable string in the
format degrees, minutes and seconds.  See also [latformat :ref](../latformat/)
and [latlongformat :ref](../latlongformat/).

## Examples

```html+jinja
<p>Lat: {{ image.exif.latitude|latformat }}
<p>Long: {{ image.exif.longitude|longformat }}
```
